abstract: Miss Lydia A. Needles, of this city, who is spending the Summer at Asbury Park, N.J., is the lady who brought up Annie Bunn, the first wife of Charles J. Guiteau. abstract: LONDON, July 8.--A special dispatch from Tunis says: "A band of native marauders stopped some caravans 20 miles from Tunis. Several tribes near Gabos have revolted.
